OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first in the west
OL,6,Fwith the odd spot of rain. Otherwise
OL,7,Fit will be dry with long bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells and feeling warm,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness then remaining
OL,13,Fdry overnight with clear spells. A
OL,14,Fmild night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FA largely dry day with bright
OL,17,Fspells. Cloud will thicken at times in
OL,18,Fthe west to bring the odd spot of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
