OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy on Monday with a little rain at
OL,7,Ffirst, but otherwise dry with plenty
OL,8,Fof sunshine. Remaining quite warm for
OL,9,Fmost but becoming cooler along the
OL,10,Feast coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
